  plot at a fairground in rural northern ireland , provisional ira volunteer fergus ( stephen rea ) and a unit of other ira members , including a woman named jude ( miranda richardson ) and led by maguire ( adrian dunbar ) , kidnap jody ( forest whitaker ) , a black british soldier , after jude lures him to a secluded area with the promise of sex .

